minimization diagrams of convex functions,</span> 7th Int. Symp.
Voronoi Diagrams in Science and Engineering (ISVD 2010), Quebec City,
Canada. <a href="http://arxiv.org/abs/0812.0607">(arXiv)</a><br>
  </li>
  <li>D. Eppstein and K.A. Wortman, <span style="font-style: italic;">Optimal
embedding
into
